            <YouTubeEmbed
                videoId="cQUAwhhC8cU"
                title="John Conway - The Game of Life and Set Theory"
            />
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl py-2">
                John Conway Distinguished Lecture - The Symmetries of Things
            </h3>
            <YouTubeEmbed
                videoId="8z6T-7ovA5Q"
                title="John Conway Distinguished Lecture - The Symmetries of Things"
            />
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl py-2">
                Samuel Broder - The Human Genome: Sequence and Assembly Was the Easy Part
            </h3>
